#: ../../modules/cost_functions/cost_functions.rst:2
msgid "Cost Functions"
msgstr "Funcions de Cost"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The :mod:`qilisdk.cost_functions` module turns "
#~ "the raw outputs returned by functionals"
#~ " into single scalar values that "
#~ "optimizers can minimize. Each cost "
#~ "function inspects the "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "produced by a backend and evaluates "
#~ "a problem-specific metric such as "
#~ "an observable expectation value or the"
#~ " energy of an abstract optimization "
#~ "model."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "El mòdul :mod:`qilisdk.cost_functions` converteix"
#~ " les sortides brutes retornades pels "
#~ "funcionals en valors escalars únics que"
#~ " els optimitzadors poden minimitzar. Cada"
#~ " funció de cost inspecciona el "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "produït per un backend i avalua "
#~ "una mètrica específica del problema, com"
#~ " ara un valor esperat d'un observable"
#~ " o l'energia d'un model d'optimització "
#~ "abstracte."

#~ msgid "You will typically use cost functions to:"
#~ msgstr "Típicament s'utilitzen les funcions de cost per:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "score intermediate iterations inside a "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram`"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "puntuar les iteracions intermèdies dins "
#~ "d'un "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram`"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "post-process "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "samples into meaningful costs"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "post-processar les mostres de "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "en costs significatius"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "translate "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "states into expectation values"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "traduir els estats de "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "en valors esperats"

#~ msgid "CostFunction Interface"
#~ msgstr "Interfície de CostFunction"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The abstract "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction` base"
#~ " class exposes a single public "
#~ "method, "
#~ ":meth:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction.compute_cost`."
#~ " It dispatches on the concrete type"
#~ " of the functional result and calls"
#~ " the appropriate protected hook:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "La classe base abstracta "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction` "
#~ "exposa un únic mètode públic, "
#~ ":meth:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction.compute_cost`."
#~ " Distribueix en funció del tipus "
#~ "concret del resultat funcional i crida"
#~ " el ganxo protegit adequat:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "It dispatches on the content of "
#~ "the "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`, "
#~ "inspecting the available readout results "
#~ "(samples, expectation values, final state) "
#~ "to compute the cost."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Distribueix en funció del contingut del"
#~ " :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`,"
#~ " inspeccionant els resultats de lectura "
#~ "disponibles (mostres, valors esperats, estat"
#~ " final) per calcular el cost."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If your workflow introduces new "
#~ "functional result types you can subclass"
#~ " :class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction` "
#~ "and register additional handlers in "
#~ "``self._handlers`` or override the protected"
#~ " methods above. Custom implementations must"
#~ " return a real or complex number "
#~ "that represents the score you want "
#~ "to optimize."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Si el vostre flux de treball "
#~ "introdueix nous tipus de resultats "
#~ "funcionals, podeu crear una subclasse de"
#~ " :class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction` "
#~ "i registrar gestors addicionals a "
#~ "``self._handlers`` o sobreescriure els mètodes"
#~ " protegits anteriors. Les implementacions "
#~ "personalitzades han de retornar un "
#~ "nombre real o complex que representi "
#~ "la puntuació que voleu optimitzar."

#~ msgid "ObservableCostFunction"
#~ msgstr "ObservableCostFunction"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.observable_cost_function.ObservableCostFunction`"
#~ " evaluates the expectation value of "
#~ "an observable against either a final "
#~ "state (from time evolution) or the "
#~ "probability distribution of sampled "
#~ "bitstrings. It accepts three interchangeable"
#~ " representations for the observable: a "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`, a symbolic "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian`, or a "
#~ "single :class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.PauliOperator`. "
#~ "Internally, all inputs are converted to"
#~ " :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` so the "
#~ "same numeric pipeline can be reused "
#~ "for both analog and digital results."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "La "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.observable_cost_function.ObservableCostFunction`"
#~ " avalua el valor esperat d'un "
#~ "observable respecte a un estat final "
#~ "(de l'evolució temporal) o a la "
#~ "distribució de probabilitats de les "
#~ "cadenes de bits mostrejades. Accepta "
#~ "tres representacions intercanviables per a "
#~ "l'observable: un :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`,"
#~ " un :class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian` "
#~ "simbòlic, o un únic "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.PauliOperator`. Internament,"
#~ " totes les entrades es converteixen a"
#~ " :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` perquè el "
#~ "mateix canal numèric es pugui "
#~ "reutilitzar tant per a resultats "
#~ "analògics com digitals."

#~ msgid "Example: expectation value from analog evolution"
#~ msgstr "Exemple: valor esperat de l'evolució analògica"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "For sampling workflows, the cost "
#~ "function iterates through the probability "
#~ "distribution exposed by "
#~ ":attr:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.probabilities`"
#~ " and accumulates the expectation value "
#~ "in the computational basis."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Per als fluxos de treball de "
#~ "mostreig, la funció de cost itera "
#~ "a través de la distribució de "
#~ "probabilitats exposada per "
#~ ":attr:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.probabilities`"
#~ " i acumula el valor esperat en "
#~ "la base computacional."

#~ msgid "ModelCostFunction"
#~ msgstr "ModelCostFunction"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.model_cost_function.ModelCostFunction`"
#~ " bridges classical optimization models with"
#~ " quantum result objects. It accepts "
#~ "any :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model` (including "
#~ "convenience subclasses such as "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`) and evaluates it"
#~ " against measured bitstrings or the "
#~ "amplitudes of a final quantum state."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "La "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.model_cost_function.ModelCostFunction`"
#~ " connecta models d'optimització clàssica "
#~ "amb objectes de resultat quàntic. "
#~ "Accepta qualsevol :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model` "
#~ "(incloent subclasses de conveniència com "
#~ "ara :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`) i l'avalua"
#~ " respecte a les cadenes de bits "
#~ "mesurades o les amplituds d'un estat "
#~ "quàntic final."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When the provided model is a "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`, the cost function"
#~ " automatically converts it into a "
#~ "Hamiltonian and computes the expectation "
#~ "value. Otherwise, it maps each sample"
#~ " to the model's variables, feeds them"
#~ " through :meth:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model.evaluate`, "
#~ "and aggregates the resulting objective "
#~ "and constraint values."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Quan el model proporcionat és un "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`, la funció de "
#~ "cost el converteix automàticament en un"
#~ " Hamiltonià i calcula el valor "
#~ "esperat. En cas contrari, associa cada"
#~ " mostra a les variables del model,"
#~ " les passa per "
#~ ":meth:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model.evaluate` i agrega "
#~ "els valors resultants d'objectiu i "
#~ "restricció."

#~ msgid "Example: scoring samples from a variational circuit"
#~ msgstr "Exemple: puntuació de mostres d'un circuit variacional"

#~ msgid "Cost Functions in Variational Programs"
#~ msgstr "Funcions de Cost en Programes Variacionals"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Variational workflows combine a parameterized"
#~ " :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.Functional`, a "
#~ "classical optimizer, and a "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction`. At"
#~ " each optimizer iteration the backend "
#~ "executes the functional, obtains a "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "object, and feeds it into the "
#~ "configured cost function to obtain the"
#~ " scalar that drives the optimization "
#~ "loop."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Els fluxos de treball variacionals "
#~ "combinen un "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.Functional` "
#~ "parametritzat, un optimitzador clàssic i "
#~ "una :class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction`."
#~ " En cada iteració de l'optimitzador, "
#~ "el backend executa el funcional, obté"
#~ " un objecte "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` "
#~ "i l'introdueix a la funció de cost"
#~ " configurada per obtenir l'escalar que "
#~ "dirigeix el bucle d'optimització."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Swapping the cost function lets you "
#~ "explore alternative objective definitions "
#~ "without touching the functional itself. "
#~ "For example, you can start with "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.observable_cost_function.ObservableCostFunction`"
#~ " to reproduce a physics-inspired "
#~ "energy expectation and later try "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.model_cost_function.ModelCostFunction`"
#~ " to include constraint penalties from "
#~ "a combinatorial problem."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Intercanviar la funció de cost permet"
#~ " explorar definicions d'objectiu alternatives "
#~ "sense modificar el propi funcional. Per"
#~ " exemple, podeu començar amb "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.observable_cost_function.ObservableCostFunction`"
#~ " per reproduir una expectativa d'energia"
#~ " inspirada en la física i "
#~ "posteriorment provar "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.model_cost_function.ModelCostFunction`"
#~ " per incloure penalitzacions de "
#~ "restriccions d'un problema combinatori."

